description_0: An indoor pulled out view of an American flag and a clock attached to a reflective ceiling. A reflection of the off frame floor is visible on the ceiling. The flag sits at the very foreground of the ceiling. The clock sits further back on the ceiling. The clock has "ROLEX" written in the center of it. The time on the analog clock reads 7:23. The frame below the clock has "ROLEX" written in green text, with gold crowns framing the text."KALIFANO" is written in white lit up letters in the bottom right corner of the frame.
description_1: An eye-level view of the top of a replica of the statue of liberty. In the foreground are metal bars crossing each other in a square pattern vertically and horizontally. The head of the statue is facing toward the bottom left corner of the image. There is a yellow light shining on the head of the statue. The torch is cut off in the ceiling, there is no flame at the top, but rather a cone shaped structure that is marble patterned and lit up. In the background of the image is a blue wall with white clouds painted on it, there are TV screens mounted to the top of the wall with an illustration of a beach, above the illustration is text that reads "MARGARITAVILLE". There is a silver wire border at the top of the wall with silver posts and a silver railing on top. Behind the border are sets of chairs and tables.
